### Test Consignment Booking API
### You can use this file with REST Client extension in VS Code or any HTTP client

### 1. Login to get token
POST http://localhost:5001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Save the accessToken from response and use in Authorization header below

### 2. Create a new consignment booking
POST http://localhost:5001/api/consignments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "from_branch_id": "b0eebc99-9c0b-4ef8-bb6d-6bb9bd380a11",
  "to_branch_id": "b1eebc99-9c0b-4ef8-bb6d-6bb9bd380a11",
  "consignor_name": "Rajesh Kumar",
  "consignor_phone": "9876543210",
  "consignor_address": "123, MG Road, Andheri East",
  "consignor_gstin": "27AABCD1234E1Z5",
