### 3. Get consignment by CN number
GET http://localhost:5001/api/consignments/MUM2025000001
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 4. List all consignments with filters
GET http://localhost:5001/api/consignments?page=1&limit=10&status=booked
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 5. Update consignment status
PUT http://localhost:5001/api/consignments/CONSIGNMENT_ID_HERE/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "status": "picked",
  "remarks": "Picked up from customer location",
  "branch_id": "b0eebc99-9c0b-4ef8-bb6d-6bb9bd380a11"
}

### 6. Get pending consignments for OGPL
GET http://localhost:5001/api/consignments/pending/ogpl?branch_id=b0eebc99-9c0b-4ef8-bb6d-6bb9bd380a11
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 7. Public tracking (no auth required)
GET http://localhost:5001/api/consignments/track/MUM2025000001